Package fr.Infuseting.util

Class JSONObject

java.lang.Object
fr.Infuseting.util.JSONObject
public class JSONObject extends Object
Represents a JSON object that stores key-value pairs. Provides methods to add, retrieve, and manipulate data with type safety.
Author:
Arthur
